name: The Daily Good 2.2.22
description:
I love numbers. 

I've been paying attention to repeating numbers and interesting number sequences for a long time. 

It seems the more I notice them the more of them I see...to an almost comical extent. (Just like the more good we notice, the more good we see). 

Today is brought to you by the number 2.

Two represents duality, two different and opposing parts.
Two also represents balance.
Two-day reminds us to find the balance between our own opposing sides.

How can you create more balance in your emotional state today?
